GameDay Live: SJSU ties it up at 10 in 2Q GameDay Live: SJSU ties it up at 10 in 2Q 
UNLV Rebels tight end Jake Phillips plays catch during warm-ups before the start of their NCAA Football game against San Jose State at Sam Boyd Stadium in Henderson Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015. Josh Holmberg/Las Vegas Review-Journal By Las Vegas Review-Journal 
After beating their rival, the Nevada Wolf Pack, the UNLV Rebels (3-2) look to carry that moment into their contest against the Spartans of San Jose State.
